snippet.title: TS!UNDERSWAP - UNDEREVENT 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
We're releasing Demo v2.0: Starlight Isles in January 2024!
Read our new Dev Update for more info: https://gamejolt.com/p/dev-update-december-2023-pncxfiut

Here's our mini-trailer from UNDEREVENT 2023 -- a presentation of UNDERTALE / DELTARUNE fan-games meant to celebrate the creative talents of this community!
FULL SHOWCASE: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ansCGZUhtVk

Video created by EllisBros
TS!UNDERSWAP by Team Switched
UNDERTALE by Toby Fox (We are not affiliated!)

--

TS!UNDERSWAP is an unofficial fan-made reimagining of Toby Fox's UNDERTALE, made by Team Switched (TS).
We aim to provide a brand new experience for fans of UNDERTALE, while staying true to its aesthetic and characters.

Like the project? Make sure to follow our progress!
Website - https://teamswitched.dev
GameJolt - https://gamejolt.com/games/tsunderswap/160094
Discord - https://discord.gg/aYNKEBzwNf
Tumblr - https://tsunderswapofficial.tumblr.com/
Twitter - https://twitter.com/tswitched
Official Wiki - https://tsunderswapofficial.wikia.com/wiki/TS!Underswap_Wiki
